title: december 8: space musk
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the first successful SpaceX launch, as well as the notorious founder of SpaceX, Elon Musk. She also chats about the beginning of the Beach Boys. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
